information.transcription:
In his Fiftieth Year
WILLIAM H.,
son of
George W. & Sarah A.
VAN DUSEN,
died
May 20, 1866.
“Blessed are the dead
do die in the Lord.”
Erected by his Brother,\nGEORGE I. VAN DUSEN.
